headline: Wells Fargo Sees Solid Outlook for MAA Despite Price Target Cut
summary: Mid-America Apartment Communities, Inc. (NYSE:MAA) is included among the 15 Blue Chip Dividend Stocks to Build a Passive Income Porfolio. Wells Fargo reduced its price target on Mid-America Apartment Communities, Inc. (NYSE:MAA) to $150 from $157 on November 26, but maintained an Overweight rating.
